sql:
SELECT match_id
FROM matches
ORDER BY match_id;

external_knowledge:
- The context assumes that the year 2023 refers to the calendar year which includes all matches played from January 1st, 2023, to December 31st, 2023; 
- A team scoring "more than one goal on average" indicates an average greater than 1 goal per match; 
- Maintaining "possession of the ball for over half the time" translates to an average possession percentage greater than 50%.
